Usage:
  app ls [--all]
  app new NAME [--force]
  app delete NAME

Commands:
  ls
    Show list of files

  new
    Pretend to create a new app

Options:
  --all
    Also show hidden files

  -f --force
    Force delete

  -h --help
    Show this help

  --version
    Show version number

Parameters:
  NAME
    The name of the repository

Environment Variables:
  SECRET
    There is no spoon

Examples:
  app ls
  app ls --all
